# GCP Artifact Registry Configuration
# Copy this file to .npmrc and update the values

# Replace these placeholders:
# - REGION: your GCP region (e.g., us-central1, asia-south1)
# - PROJECT_ID: your GCP project ID
# - REPOSITORY_NAME: your Artifact Registry repository name

@rappit:registry=https://REGION-npm.pkg.dev/PROJECT_ID/REPOSITORY_NAME/
//REGION-npm.pkg.dev/PROJECT_ID/REPOSITORY_NAME/:always-auth=true
